OL,3,CBonnie Tyler remains 'seriously ill
OL,4,Cbut stable' at hospital in Portugal
OL,6,FSinger Bonnie Tyler remains "seriously
OL,7,Fill" but in a "stable" condition at a
OL,8,Fhospital near her home in Faro,
OL,9,FPortugal.
OL,11,FIt comes after news that she had been
OL,12,Fplaced in an induced coma to aid in
OL,13,Fher recovery from emergency intestinal
OL,14,Fsurgery on Wednesday 7 May.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday (12 May), a statement
OL,17,Fposted on the singer's official
OL,18,Fwebsite said that doctors are
OL,19,F"positive" she will make a full
OL,20,Frecovery.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
