OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778595071
OL,3,CBonnie Tyler remains 'seriously ill
OL,4,Cbut stable' at hospital in Portugal
OL,6,FIn a statement, her spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"As of this morning, Bonnie remains
OL,8,Fseriously ill but stable in a hospital
OL,9,Fin Faro; however, her doctors are
OL,10,Fstill positive that she will make a
OL,11,Ffull recovery."
OL,13,FThe singer's family expressed that
OL,14,Fthey have been "disappointed" by
OL,15,F"lurid and untrue rumours" published
OL,16,Fby the media.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
