OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778595071
OL,3,CBonnie Tyler remains 'seriously ill
OL,4,Cbut stable' at hospital in Portugal
OL,6,FThe statement concluded: "We ask that
OL,7,Fthe media cease to speculate or
OL,8,Fpublish wild rumours, which simply
OL,9,Fserve to upset her family, friends,
OL,10,Fand many fans. We ask again for
OL,11,Fprivacy and decency at this difficult
OL,12,Ftime."
OL,14,FTyler, whose real name is Gaynor
OL,15,FHopkins, achieved international fame
OL,16,Fin the 1980s with the release of her
OL,17,Fsingle Total Eclipse Of The Heart,
OL,18,Fwhich shot to the top of the charts in
OL,19,Fthe UK and US.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
