OL,3,CBonnie Tyler remains 'seriously ill
OL,4,Cbut stable' at hospital in Portugal
OL,6,FThe Grammy-nominated star is due to
OL,7,Ftour Europe later this year to mark 50
OL,8,Fyears since the release of her 1976
OL,9,Fbreakthrough hit Lost In France, which
OL,10,Fentered the charts across Europe.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
